Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(653,541)}Yuma... Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III, his conviction is for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know whether we will win for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to know that guy's true feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I truly desire to have a {\i1}real{\i0} duel with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you can learn everything from the opponent through dueling. Aren't you the one who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you only have 4 heart pieces so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so whether you can qualify for the Finals of the WDC all depends on this duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! All of you guys have come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cat{\i0}, isn't this the final battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to here just to see Yuma's face when he loses instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, we can't miss this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you guys actually thought I would lose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding, that's not what we think!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.14,0:01:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all expect you to win, Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering you already got this far... there's no doubt you're the strongest duelist among us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.29,0:01:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can definitely become the champion, {\i1}cat{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, V?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look quite distressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to underestimate the power of the messenger from the Astral World.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry. III will win for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he already acquired strength equivalent of the pain he just endured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A power that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I get closer, I stretch my hand out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}towards that shining light leading towards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I dream of a world that expands from my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't a clue of where things like dreams and hopes are at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I run looking for it, I still can't seem to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I have fallen into a gap of truth and lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, our grand tale has yet to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's move on towards tomorrow, \Neven if our road begins to fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will jump forward, before all my\N strength completely drains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The closer I get, the further it becomes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that truth that I must seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's to find hope that we desire from a future unseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With a heart stronger than anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll learn to keep running up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the strength to win any battle, \Ndespite just how weak I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My purpose is to find,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with these invaluable friends of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future of the world expanding\N from my feet with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(502,504)}Number 47: Yuma Gives Up!?\N The Stolen "Bring It To 'Em!""
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(627,514)}Sorry for the wait, III!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, in order to defeat you, I just obtained a new power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the encounter with you and your family, I confirmed something
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I may have to defeat you in order to get back my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to know your true feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may become friends after the battle and able to learn everything from each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is dueling!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who stands on that side are all my friends who created bonds with me through dueling!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus I strongly believe there must be such bond between you and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel disk, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel disk, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-gazer, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR-Vision: link established.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After obtaining power from Tron, in my current state...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Astral, I can clearly see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are the one who's been assisting Yuma all this time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But even with you as my opponent, I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Field Magic OOPart City Babylon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I special summon the OOParts Monster Tula Guardian!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When there is a field Magic on my field, I can special summon this card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I normal summon the OOParts Monster Golden Shuttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Golden Shuttle's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once per turn, I can increase this monster's level by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overlay the LV5 Tula Guardian and Golden Shuttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I build the Overlay Network with these 2 monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself, No. 33!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OOParts Super Weapon Machu Mach!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He already summoned Machu Mach... that fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card face-down, and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, try to beat me, Yuma! With your dueling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To duel in order to hurt someone is not dueling at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the 'Bring it to 'Em' my father has taught me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Bring it to 'Em'...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame that I won't allow you to use that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, III!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so hasty, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:08:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He already has Machu Mach on his field. The top priority right now is to build defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Plus that momentum of his...\Nseems quite different than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you can't beat him by attacking recklessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I set a monster in face-down defense position!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And set one card, ending my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic card from my hand, Sarcophagus of Palanque!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When there is a card that includes "OOPart" in its card name on my field, I can draw 2 cards from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, during the turn I activated a normal Magic, I can special summon this monster from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, OOParts monster Aztec Mask Golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... that's III's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like my favorite card! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aztec... Mask... Golem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Aztec Mask Golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Palanque Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I expected, it's Gogogo Golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If both of their ATK are 1500, then this battle is a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gogogo Golem won't be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, when Gogogo Golem is in defense position, once per turn, it cannot be destroyed by battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way I can survive Machu Mach's attack as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My goal isn't battle at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I normal summon the OOParts monster Cabrera's Catapult!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster with zero ATK?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Cabrera's Catapult's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By releasing one monster on my field,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During this turn, the ATK of one monster my opponent controls will become zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the curse, Gogogo Golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gogogo Golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting troublesome. This combo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, I activate Machu Mach's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Machu Mach's effect is, when a monster's ATK changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once per turn, by detaching one overlay unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the equal to the changed amount will be inflicted as damage to my opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words 1800 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infinity Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Cabrera's Catapult just used its effect, it switched to Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I will end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This III guy, his duel is completely different than before! Just what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... if this is his ace, I got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is {\i1}my{\i0} duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to win this with my own dueling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate the Equipment Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Equipment Magic Bound Wand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then once per turn, Gagaga Magician can become any level between 1 to 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I already said I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I change Gagaga Magician's level to 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Bound Wand's effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The equipped Spellcaster monster gains ATK equal to its level times 100!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!! But won't that trigger Machu Mach's effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He won't use Machu Mach's last Overlay Unit for this small amount of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Gagaga Magician, attack Cabrera's Catapult!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already saw through your attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap activate! Costa Rican Stone Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can negate the opposing monster's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that monster cannot declare an attack during your next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How's that, Astral?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, set the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Geez, it's all your fault!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card, and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, Gagaga Magician's level returns to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ATK raised by Bound Wand's effect will go down as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Field Spell OOParts Ancient City Babylon's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once per turn, by removing one OOParts monster in my graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can special summon one OOParts monster with same level from my graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I banish Golden Shuttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, pull Aztec Mask Golem out from graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I change Cabrera's Catapult to attack position!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once again set Aztec Golem as ammunition!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... III...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet! It's fine as long as the monsters become my pawns!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to like OOParts so much... but look what you did to that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of price I have to pay, I have to defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Cabrera's Catapult's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another combo with Machu Mach's effect would...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... would make Yuma only have 300 LP left!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, if he was attacked by Machu Mach...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0} would lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use Gagaga Rush, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ri... right! Trap activate, Gagaga Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card's effect is, when Gagaga Magician was targeted by an effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it will negate its activation, and destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And inflict damage to my opponent equal to the ATK or DEF, whichever is higher, of the monster who used that effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabrera's DEF is 1800, eat this damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!\NNow their LP are even!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Don't tell me you planned that since the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now his duel is too fixated on winning, which sometimes can make him extra cautious,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to a reckless guy like you, he is much easier to analyze in terms of strategies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you said something unnecessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will win like this! Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, it won't be enough just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will let that guy find his true inner self through this duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:16:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma's 'Bring it to 'Em'... and Astral's advanced tactics,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me their combined power exceeds mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III, sacrificing OOPart's monster, that's not your dueling at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what kind of power you did got, but you should at least duel in your own {\i1}style{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A happy person like you, surrounded with friends, would never understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the true agony and pain I've felt... The feeling of having no one by your side...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III... ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally managed to find my family, but it's already falling apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has become twisted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so... I still wish to protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, you annoy me! Your actions are an eyesore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:16:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall into the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? The Lord's Key?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To win against Yuma Tsukumo, having strong Numbers is by far not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His father, Kazuma Tsukumo was a brave adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a person's son should not be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Power of the Crest I gave to III will take away the most precious things from Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, what's waiting for him is... a world of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what am I trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I forgot the most important thing to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come, climb up, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can I climb on something this steep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, you can climb on this! (**), Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? What did he just say? What did you say, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\b1}Dad!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Scary, so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey... you don't want to challenge that, Tsukumo-{\i0}kun{\i1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't wanna... it's so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can I jump on something that high anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But how would you know that without challenging it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that... without doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't do it... can't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nice! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are great, good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You sissy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The card you were afraid of was nothing but an Equipment Magic card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh my, what a boring duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To summarize, that was an unworthy duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Such a cowardly guy is a disgrace to duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Scary... so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry... Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Scary... So scary... Everyone is looking down on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Geez... \N- What an annoying guy he is... !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You would become a coward as well if you are trying to approach him... \N- Such a disgrace of duelists!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Scary... Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why would it be this scary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's gone... Something important to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...has disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuma, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary... so scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I duel like this anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What happened, Yuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously it's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I possibly win...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... This all is the power of the crest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:21:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 'Bring it to 'Em' has already disappeared from his heart, which means Yuma can no longer see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Yuma! Don't be devoured by the evil power, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral, I won't allow you to interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This crest also has the power to seal {\i1}you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral, disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, your 'Bring it to 'Em' has already disappeared from your memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there is no 'Bring it to 'Em', you cannot see neither Astral nor the Lord's Key.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are no longer a match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Machu Mach! Attack Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:21:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma! Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma! Yuma!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, disappear within the darkness of despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.06,0:22:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone gave me some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I was able to paint a rainbow with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.28,0:22:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to become someone perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even with me suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't seem to grasp victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.67,0:22:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must be having some kind of weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.05,0:23:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But If I must fulfill this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.59,0:23:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I don't mind being laughed at for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.55,0:23:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since it's because your limits are decided on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll show it, overcoming it to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, I'm aiming for the big blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For all of its glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Freesia of Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of those countless flower petals
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.33,0:23:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They came at the expense of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}me being able to reach those heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, even though I lost my way today,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still yearn for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.01,0:23:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Freesia of Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:23:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to power of the crest, Yuma has lost his 'Bring it to 'Em'.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:23:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no more fighting spirit within his eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.31,0:23:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that heart of a challenger which vows never give up has also vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.17,0:24:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then even I too...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.49,0:24:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember it, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.77,0:24:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I will surrender the duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.87,0:24:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the last of my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time in Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!\N - Astral... dies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.36,0:24:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.63,0:24:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.54,0:24:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monster we're introducing this week is Drum Devil Tenten Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can absorb the opponent's Overlay Units and use them as your own power!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.09,0:24:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will use Tenten Tempo to give Yuma a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.73,0:24:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's eas-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.61,0:24:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as three tens.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.92,0:24:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
